=======

chmod [change mod]

u => user[owner]

x => execute

chmod u+x filename [give owner execute permission of that file].

=======

chmod g+x filename [give group execute permission of that file].

=======

chmod o+x filename gives [everyone the execute permissions on that file].

=======

They can be used together like

chmod u+x, g+x, o+x filename [This gives, owner, group, and everyone else execute permissions on that file].

=======

Taking away privileges

chmod u-x, g-x filename [takes, owner, and group execute permissions away].

=======

read = 4

write = 2

execute = 1
